channel.description:
[center][img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img] Yhlo, Welcome to meh thread :) First I Made One To Zero On 01-01-07! I Retired It On 15 May 07
About Me, Im A Boy. From Teh England Let's Get On With the Account.
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[b][u]Stats when i made thread[/u][/b] [IMG]http://img410.imageshack.us/img410/7342/stats08161424rh8.png[/img] Combat 45
[b][u]Current Stats[/u][/b] [IMG]http://img410.imageshack.us/img410/7342/stats08161424rh8.png[/img]
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[b][u]Goals And Level Ups[/u][/b]
[u]Short Term Goals[/u] 60 Attack 85 strength 70 Magic 70 Ranged
[u]Non Combat Related Goals[/u] Mith gloves Desert Treasure Monkey Madness Horror from the deep Higher Skills (Atleast 1 99 skill, Not combat eg. Cooking)
[u]Long Term Goals[/u] 60 Attack 99 Strength 94 Magic 80 Ranged
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[u]Latest Pk:[/u] [b]OBBY CAPE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!![/b] Lol, this story is the funniest by miles Basically, i was like, pking..No skull, i run in, check my msn convo with My gf, then i see obby cape and death message LOL [IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u114/FookItAll/pkftwwwww.jpg[/img] Loot: [IMG]http://i166.photobucket.com/albums/u114/FookItAll/obbycapepk.jpg[/img]
Blanked out a few things, secretz :)
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[u][b]Pk Gallery[/b][/u] Gf, wasn't a dm just a friendly fight, Didn't telly or run on low food, Respect <3 Blanked out some of my invent, twas a secret invent for this dm.
[img]http://img154.imageshack.us/img154/9352/pkftwik7.jpg[/img]
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[img]http://img178.imageshack.us/img178/2156/1217319908stoppjinuh9.png[/img][u][b]My Honour Code[/b][/u][img]http://img178.imageshack.us/img178/2156/1217319908stoppjinuh9.png[/img]
To Be Honest I [u]Do Not [/u] Believe In Honour. But I [u]DO[/u] Believe In Respect.
I Do: ~Pray Vs 1 Itemers ~Pk In What I Want ~Pk Everywhere I Want ~Try To Say Gl - Gf Every Fight ~Take Risks ~Carry T tabs, to telly from Pjers. ~Die
I Do Not: ~Pj ~Farcast ~Pray Suddenly In A Fight ~Telly Out Of Edge-Unless pjers. ~Safe Eat
[img]http://img167.imageshack.us/img167/3070/divider08df6.gif[/img]
[u][b]Bank Picture:[/b][/u]
[IMG]http://img201.imageshack.us/img201/894/stats08105636hi1.png[/img]

Thanks for reading, Post please?
-Ollie[/center]
